conflicts wherever possible" through the "development of its peace-
keeping role".
</P>
<P>
Ranieri stressed, however, that despite the wish to avert
Moscow's isolation, "it is evident" that should the military
offensive continue unabated, international financial organizations
and the EU would have to review their joint cooperation strategy
with Russia. 
