assistance to Chechen refugees who fled their hometowns during
recent Russian military operations in Chechnya.
</P>
<P>
During his stay in Iran, Ivanov stressed that Chechen issue was
an internal affair of Russian Federation, denying any attacks on
Chechnya and massacre of civilians.
</P>
<P>
Before anything else it should be said that no such attacks
have been or can be made on Chechnya because the territory is part
of the Russian Federation, he said.
</P>
<P>
Ivanov said that Russian operations are not against Muslims,
but terrorists, irrespective of their nationality or religious
affiliation. 
</P>
