expansion effort targeted at western China.
</P>
<P>
Described as the first showcase of the company for its latest
concept in telecommunications, the town is designed to introduce
Motorola's state-of-the-art telecom technology to Chinese
customers at the earliest possible time, according to a senior
executive.
</P>
<P>
