campaign against the killer disease, AIDS, was marked for the
first time in the Somali capital Mogadishu on Wednesday.
</P>
<P>
Hundreds of youth groups, Somalia's joint health authority and
representatives from the World Health Organization (WHO) have
gathered in the IIDA women center of North Mogadishu commemorating
