the disease has no borders and spreads faster than the imagination
of the people.
</P>
<P>
In Mogadishu, posters and pamphlets have been distributed
carrying important messages against the spread of AIDS.
</P>
<P>
Fuji said his agency supplied the necessary reagents for
screening the blood for HIV viruses especially in the hospitals
where the blood donations and transfusions continue. 
