participate in the demonstration," said Albert K. Y. Lam, director
of the department.
</P>
<P>
Deputy director of the department Alex Au said that the Hong
Kong government will invite the PLA to join in the demonstration
every year.
</P>
<P>
An S-70 helicopter from the Hong Kong Government Flying
Services also took part in the operation.
</P>
<P>
The Civil Aid Service took part by providing mountain rescue
and casualty evacuation preparation from the hill side. 
